window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A tale of ambition and power</b></p> <p>A soul from Earth awakens as Seventh Princess Adelheid of the Vuldar Empire. With a weak body but a monstrous reservoir of mana that threatens her very life, Adelheid engraves an oath into her very soul. She shall seize the throne at all costs, but with ambitious cousins and discontent nobles, her father and brother are far from her only rivals.</p> <p>Experience Adelheid's journey through victory and loss to achieve her deepest desires.</p>"; 
